Browser
- Fennec because ublock Origin

Camera
- Install Google Camera from Play Store
- Hold shutter = start capturing video
- Normal Mode
    - Night Sight Auto
    - Enable RAW option
    - Top Shot Auto
    - Full image
    - Save location
    - Volume buttons are shutter
        - Combined with double tap power to open camera = super fast access to taking photos/videos
        - Can hold as well to immediately start taking video
- Video
    - 4K 60
- Night Sight
    - Only use for astrophotography

Location
- Sandboxed Google Play
    - Reroute location requests to the OS = on (enabled by default)
    - Google Location Accuracy = on (disabled by default)
- GmsCompat needs access to location all the time